<P><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="5"><b>On the picket line</b></font></P>
<p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">March 14, 2003 | Pages 10 and 11</font></p>

<font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3"><P><STRONG>OTHER STORIES BELOW:</STRONG><BR>
